Obviously, this is a sample. This will fail in the `parametrizedUsingValue` test method.

`@BeforeClass` exists, but it requires the setup to be static and doesn&#39;t guarantee any cleanup of the static members you initialize. That can be a problem in actual tests, even though it would not be problem in the sample above.

Why does `@Before` not apply to `@ParametrizedTest`. Is there any way of working around that without compromising independence of tests?

